Class SimuContextImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl
      org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.BasicEObjectImpl
          org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl

                  com.interpss.simu.impl.SimuContextImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
NameTag, SimuContext, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject
public class SimuContextImpl
extends NameTagImpl
implements SimuContext

An implementation of the model object 'Network'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Net Type
  • Resource Type
  • Msg Hub
  • Aclf Net
  • Acsc Net
  • DStability Net
  • Dist Net
  • Opf Net
  • Loadflow Algorithm
  • Simple Fault Algorithm
  • Dyn Simu Algorithm
  • Dclf Algorithm
